title: Episode 225: Live Tour DC (w Donnell Rawlings, Rico Nasty, DJ QuickSilva, Mechie So Crazy)
itunes:title: Episode 225: Live Tour DC (w Donnell Rawlings, Rico Nasty, DJ QuickSilva, Mechie So Crazy)
description:
DJ QuickSilva, Donnell Rawlings, Rico Nasty, and Mechie so Crazy join the ladies of Lip Service in Washington DC for the Lip Service Live Tour. We also brought in Tasha the intuitive to give readings for each guest. Rico opens up about spitting in fans mouth, Mechie speaks on his sex tape with Blac Chyna, and much more. Enjoy!
